headline: Texas AG investigating Kellogg over ‘unhealthy’ cereal claims
summary: The review comes as Donald Trump and HHS Secretary Robert F. Kennedy Jr. pressure food companies to improve their offerings as part of their Make America Healthy Again initiative.
